abstract: Talks between Georgia and Russia on Russia's accession to World Trade Organization end with no agreement, and little time remains if Russia is to Join WTO by end of 2011.
snippet: Talks between Georgia and Russia on Russia’s accession to the World Trade Organization ended with no agreement on Thursday.
lead_paragraph: Talks between Georgia and Russia on Russia’s accession to the World Trade Organization ended with no agreement on Thursday.

headline.main: Russia and Georgia Trade Talks Stymied
